snippet.title: Indie Heroes Collection 3 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Evercade VS.
Like on the second Indie Heroes Collection, we get games previously featured as part of the Game of the Month program during 2023, alongside cart exclusive games. This time around, this cart contains two native games for your enjoyment, alongside the 8-bit and 16-bit games. Oh, and we see two certain pals making a return on this cart.

Games on the cart:
00:00:18 - Alien Cat 2: Enhanced Edition (SNES)
00:08:18 - Big2Small (GBC)
00:19:42 - Bone Marrow (MD)
00:38:20 - Bubble Seahorse Adventures (Native)
00:48:00 - Chew Chew Mimic (NES)
00:54:30 - Chibi Monster Br4wl (NES)
00:57:42 - Donut Dodo (Native)
01:03:01 - Doodle World Redrawn (NES)
01:06:02 - Magic and Legend: Time Knights (GB)
01:16:55 - Orebody: Binder's Tale (NES)
01:23:20 - Skate Cat (NES)
01:30:52 - The Little Tales of Alexandria (GB)
01:43:14 - Thunder Paw (MD)

Alien Cat 2 (C) Repa Games
Bone Marrow (C) HugePixel
Thunder Paw (C) SergioPoverony
Alien Cat 2: Enhanced Edition, Bone Marrow and Thunder Paw ports by PSCD Games
Big2Small (C) mdsteele / The Retro Room Games
Bubble Seahorse Adventures (C) Philip Hassey
Chew Chew Mimic (C) Lowtek Games / Rigg'd Games
Donut Dodo (C) pixel games SARL-S
Doodle World Redrawn (C) Nate Peters
Magic and Legend: Time Knights (C) Legendary Monkey Magic / The Retro Room Games
Orebody: Binder's Tale (C) Orebody Inc. / John Vanderhoef
Skate Cat (C) SJ Games
The Little Tales of Alexandria (C) MrE
Chibi Monster Br4wl (C) Dale Coop Studio
